#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""gcm - Git Commit Message generator (free, via Groq API).

Doc staged diff, nho LLM viet message Conventional Commits, review roi commit.
Khong can API tra phi (Groq free tier). Thuan stdlib, khong can pip install.

Staging:
  gcm -s             Chon file de stage (nhap so)
  gcm -t             Chon file kieu TUI (mui ten + space, 'd' xem diff)
  gcm -a             git add -A truoc khi sinh

Message:
  gcm -m "hint"      Them ngu canh/goi y cho message
  gcm --vi / --en    Message tieng Viet / English
  gcm --model NAME   Doi model cho lan chay nay

Commit & push:
  gcm -y             Commit luon, khong hoi
  gcm --push         Tu push sau khi commit
  gcm --amend        Sua (reword) commit gan nhat
  gcm -p             Chi in message, khong commit

Khac:
  gcm config         Xem config hien tai
  gcm -u             Tu cap nhat gcm len ban moi nhat (git pull)
  gcm -h             Tro giup

Khi review: [Enter] commit . [p] commit+push . [e] sua . [r] tao lai . [n] huy
Neu chua stage gi ma working tree co thay doi, gcm tu mo bo chon file.
Lockfile/binary van duoc commit nhung khong gui noi dung cho LLM.

Config (~/.config/gcm/config, dang key = value):
  api_key = gsk_...      key free tai https://console.groq.com/keys
  lang = vi | en         ngon ngu mac dinh cua message
  model = <ten model>    mac dinh: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
  tui = true | false     mac dinh chon file kieu TUI
  push = ask | always | never
Env: GROQ_API_KEY, GCM_MODEL (uu tien hon config). Flag uu tien hon tat ca.
"""
